<task id="task_bdv_znl_jp">
    <title>Editing tags using the CWRC-Writer toolbar</title>
    <shortdesc>You can edit any of the tags that pre-exist in the template or that you have added to
        the document. This also allows you to add additional information to the tags in your
        document (E.g. next, rend, etc.).</shortdesc>
    <prolog product="CWRC-Writer">
